title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Whiskey
description:
A shot of all access fire for riders who take on everything the mountain can throw at you. A blended brew of durability, versatility, and System Rocker performance that makes this board ideal for the cross platform experience: park, trees, speed, steeps, powder, and more.
To learn more about the Whiskey visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/whiskey/
